\/strong><\/p>\n<p>You can also specify whether you want us to automatically email invitations to the meeting participants. The invitations will contain a link that participants can click on to join the meeting. You can also specify whether you would like us to send a reminder to the meeting participants an hour before the meeting starts.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"http:\/\/blog.screenleap.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/05\/meetings.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1400\" src=\"http:\/\/blog.screenleap.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/05\/meetings.png\" alt=\"meetings\" width=\"618\" height=\"209\" srcset=\"https:\/\/blog.screenleap.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/05\/meetings.png 618w, https:\/\/blog.screenleap.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2014\/05\/meetings-300x101.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 618px) 100vw, 618px\" \/><\/a><\/p>\n<p>To start a meeting, simply click on the\u00a0<strong>Start<\/strong>\u00a0button for the meeting.<\/p>\n<p>The scheduled meetings feature is available on our <a href=\"https:\/\/www.screenleap.com\/signup\/user?accountType=PRO&amp;paymentPeriod=12\">Pro<\/a> and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.screenleap.com\/signup\/company?paymentPeriod=12\">Premium<\/a> Accounts. All users with a Screenleap account will be able to try out the meetings feature until June 16 for free.\u00a0<a href=\"https:\/\/www.screenleap.com\/login?redirectUrl=%2Fmeetings\" target=\"_blank\">Sign in now<\/a>\u00a0to give it a try.<\/p>\n<p>We hope the meetings feature makes it even easier for you to share your screen. Please let us know what you think of it!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>We are excited to announce the launch of a long-awaited feature: you can now schedule screen shares in advance using our meetings feature. Previously, you had to start a screen share before you could get\u00a0the share code and share link needed\u00a0to share with your viewers. Now, you can send the share links in adv